snippet.title: Assassin’s Creed 3 | Mobile Game Android Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Mobile Game
Assassin's Creed 3 - Love the hidden murders and the history of the assassins in general? This game is defined to the liking of all fans of the classics. It certainly is not a super new 3D, but still a good story and dynamic gameplay are guaranteed to you. Because this is a ported version of the game, the management is simple and you will not have to install anything extra.

Features:
A fascinating plot
Simple operation
